.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢連冷氣同熱水爐都識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (利申返佢係有牌)<br />\n我細細過真係以為男人識整電器係常識黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點之原來唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n深感認同<br />\n老豆係做文職，但以前讀工科所以屋企細至電器電線 大至門較外牆所有嘢都自己整<br />\n<br />\n所以一直都覺得所有男人都應該識呢啲嘢，但結果身邊好多男人連最簡單電腦嗰啲都唔識。我自己學都學咗了</blockquote><br />\n講起電腦野，大個開始學自己砌機個啲先發現其實老豆其實唔熟依啲野，但細個個陣有咩用唔到唔洗整佢都有求必應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c275610e5b88bbbc330cf360178cf50d40b32bff","tid":429843,"uid":31641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T01:10:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>徒手打甲由依d唔講啦<br />\n老豆係水電工，屋企所有電器 燈 水喉 廁所入面既野都係佢整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢連冷氣同熱水爐都識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (利申返佢係有牌)<br />\n我細細過真係以為男人識整電器係常識黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點之原來唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n深感認同<br />\n老豆係做文職，但以前讀工科所以屋企細至電器電線 大至門較外牆所有嘢都自己整<br />\n<br />\n所以一直都覺得所有男人都應該識呢啲嘢，但結果身邊好多男人連最簡單電腦嗰啲都唔識。我自己學都學咗了</blockquote><br />\n講起電腦野，大個開始學自己砌機個啲先發現其實老豆其實唔熟依啲野，但細個個陣有咩用唔到唔洗整佢都有求必應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔識*"},{"pid":"ba2570d0981ee52a26d337f94d170db9fda09be8","tid":429843,"uid":82441,"like